act: Board of Agriculture and Fisheries Act 1909
section_title: Power to appoint second secretary to the Board of Agriculture and Fisheries.

act: Board of Agriculture and Fisheries Act 1909
section_text: 2 This Act may be cited as the Board of Agriculture and Fisheries Act 1909; and the  Board of Agriculture and Fisheries Acts 1889 and 1903 and this Act may be cited together as the Board of Agriculture and Fisheries Acts 1889 to 1909.
